item.title: CVE-2019-11062|2024-09-17T00:40:32.733Z -- sunnet -- wmpro
item.description: The SUNNET WMPro v5.0 and v5.1 for eLearning system has OS Command Injection via "/teach/course/doajaxfileupload.php". The target server can be exploited without authentication.
